  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then that was the end of April.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were transported by train from this Kaufering camp to Kaufering camp number one, which was only a few miles, but no one could walk.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we figured that they're taking us to finish us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they took us to that camp number one because from there they had the railroad going to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The company that I worked for was a German company called [GERMAN], the builders.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "To my great, painful surprise when I was not too long ago in Munich, I saw a big sign, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I thought they would be-- that a company like this wouldn't exist.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I know Krupp exists, and others, but here I was involved with them on a daily basis, and they employed slave labor.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But anyway, when we came to this camp number one, that's where we already heard the Americans guns.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I saw this was blinking, so I--",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
